# Derived model: qwen3:8b with a 16K context baked in.
# WHY: Goose's Ollama provider forces num_ctx=4096 regardless of the server's
# OLLAMA_CONTEXT_LENGTH. At 4K, Goose's tool-definition system prompt overflows and
# the small model deadlocks/loops. Baking num_ctx into a derived model is the only
# override Goose respects (verified: `ollama ps` then reports CONTEXT 16384).
# Created by goose/setup-models.sh as `qwen3-goose`. Guide: life/guides/local-llm.md
FROM qwen3:8b
PARAMETER num_ctx 16384
